    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2383220/extras/c918700cb9bd4a77a25f127304137204.poster.avif?t=1769703007\" width=600 height=98 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2383220/extras/c918700cb9bd4a77a25f127304137204.webm?t=1769703007\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2383220/extras/c918700cb9bd4a77a25f127304137204.mp4?t=1769703007\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>在《神探：星扉失踪案》中，你将扮演一位警探，调查三起奇怪的失踪案。在这些案件中，失踪者都和一个叫“星扉”的组织签订了契约。在《神探：星扉失踪案》中，你将扮演一位警探，调查三起奇怪的失踪案。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2383220/extras/c8b8c5f35f02930aaee24511654716b7.poster.avif?t=1769703007\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2383220/extras/c8b8c5f35f02930aaee24511654716b7.webm?t=1769703007\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2383220/extras/c8b8c5f35f02930aaee24511654716b7.mp4?t=1769703007\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>在这些案件中，失踪者都和一个叫“星扉”的组织签订了契约。每个案件的情况完全不同，但是它们之间似乎又有着某种联系。作为一名警探，你的任务就是解决案件，并找出它们之间的关联。作为一名警探，你必须在犯罪现场收集你发现的所有证据，这些证据之后会帮助你破案。<br><br>一切都很重要，细节、物品、对话，你需要有敏锐的洞察力才能推进侦破。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2383220/extras/829d59031a72d33d999dd31b5bf5a654.poster.avif?t=1769703007\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2383220/extras/829d59031a72d33d999dd31b5bf5a654.webm?t=1769703007\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2383220/extras/829d59031a72d33d999dd31b5bf5a654.mp4?t=1769703007\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>特征</strong></h2><br>-三个不同的案件。<br>-你必须标记证据并拍照。<br>-一旦你获得了证据，你必须到办公室里整理证据才能破案。<br><br>《神探：星扉失踪案》黑暗而令人毛骨悚然的基调，展现出了当代社会华丽外表之下的现实。<br><br>偵探：Stella Porta案，黑暗而可怕，顯示出未經過濾的當代社會現實。",
